Utilities shutoff moratorium start: The CUSP team is grateful to collaborate with the research team led by Emily A Benfer, JD LLM to report state-level utilities policy data. To access the full COVID-19 Eviction Moratoria & Housing Policy dataset, please contact benfere@wfu.edu.
Benfer EA, Koehler R, Alexander AK, Adam K, Mark A. COVID-19 Eviction Moratoria & Housing Policy: Federal, State, Commonwealth, and Territory. Published 2020.
